text: Vicarello may refer to: == Places == *Vicarello, Bracciano, a village in the metropolitan city of Rome, Italy *Vicarello, Collesalvetti, a village in the province of Livorno, Italy == Other uses == *Castle of Vicarello, a castle in Cinigiano, province of Grosseto, Tuscany *Vicarello Cups, archaeological finds from Vicarello, Bracciano
